{"author":" <simon.a.chiang@gmail.com>","title":"Pulls create unwanted local branch.","date":"2010-04-26T22:14:19-06:00","tags":["open"],"type":"issue","content":"The issue is this line in repo.rb:\r\n\r\ncode.. \r\n  git.fetch({}, remote, \"#{remote_branch}:#{tracking_branch}\")\r\n\r\np. Which should be:\r\n\r\ncode.. \r\n  git.fetch({}, remote, \"#{remote_branch}:remotes/#{tracking_branch}\")","at":"50a0e4421b0951518c5097ea18e9ed717a1730b3"}